<div class="header">
    <img class="logo pull-left" src="/plugin/thespaghettidetective/static/img/logo-square.png" /> <h3>The Spaghetti Detective (Beta)</h3>
</div>
<h5><a href="https://thespaghettidetective.com/">The Spaghetti Detective</a> is an AI-based failure detection for 3D printer.</h5>
<p>Check out the <a href="https://thespaghettidetective.com/guide.html">Setup Guide</a>. Also our <a href="https://thespaghettidetective.com/privacy.html">Privacy Policy</a> and <a href="https://thespaghettidetective.com/terms.html">Terms of Use</a>.</p>
<p>The Spaghetti Detective is currently in beta testing. You can sign up a free beta testing account <strong>before March 31st</strong>.
If you feel adventurous, head to <a href="https://github.com/TheSpaghettiDetective/TheSpaghettiDetective">our source code</a> and set up your own server.</p>
<hr />
<form class="form-horizontal">
    <h4>Secret token</h4>
    <div>Secret token is the key to make sure only you can access data in your account, not anyone else. Click <a href="#">here</a> to find the secrete token and copy it to the box below.</div>
    <div class="input-append token-input">
        <input id="auth-token-input" type="text" class="input-block-level" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.thespaghettidetective.auth_token">
        <button id="test-auth-token" class="btn" type="button"><i class="fa fa-spinner fa-spin" data-bind="visible: testWebcamStreamUrlBusy" style="display: none;"></i> Test</button>
    </div>
    <div id="std-api-status">&nbsp; </div>
    <div class="advanced-header"><a href="#" class="muted" onclick="$(this).children().toggleClass('icon-caret-right icon-caret-down').parent().parent().next().slideToggle('fast')"><i class="icon-caret-right"></i>Adavanced</a></div>
    <div class="hide">
        <div class="control-group">
            <label class="control-label">{{ _('Server Address') }}</label>
            <div class="controls">
                <input type="text" class="input-block-level" id="endpoint-prefix" disabled data-bind="value: settings.plugins.thespaghettidetective.endpoint_prefix">
                <div class="form-check" style="margin-top: 8px;">
                  <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" value="" id="custom-server" style="margin-top: 0px;">
                  <label class="form-check-label" for="custom-server" style="display: inline">
                    I have my own TSD server (don't check this unless you know what you are doing).
                  </label>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</form>
